title: Cubans flock to Colombia for U.S. visas
text:
Cubans flock to Colombia for U.S. visas 11:06am GMT - 02:00 
After the Trump administration stopped processing U.S. visas in Havana hundreds of Cubans are flying to Colombia for visa interviews at the U.S. embassy there, an extra layer of cost and bureaucracy in an already complex affair. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
